<topic id="withdraw" xml:lang="en-us">
<title>Software discontinuance of support: <tm trademark="IBM" tmtype="reg">IBM</tm> Sterling Data Exchange select products</title>
<topic id="topic_ddl_3gt_51c">
<title>Overview</title>
<body>
<p><tm trademark="IBM" tmtype="reg">IBM</tm> Sterling Data Exchange is discontinuing support of select releases for multiple products. Clients with active maintenance are eligible to upgrade to the latest product releases and thereby benefit from security updates, performance enhancements, automation improvements to client and partner onboarding, modernized user interfaces and RESTful APIs, as well as hybrid cloud deployment options. For more information, contact your <tm trademark="IBM" tmtype="reg">IBM</tm> representative or <tm trademark="IBM" tmtype="reg">IBM</tm> Business Partner.</p>
</body>
</topic>
