<topic id="topic_b5r_dyq_f1c">
<title>Technical support</title>
<body>
<p>Technical support continues to be available based on the announced lifecycle policy, as detailed
on the <xref href="https://www.ibm.com/support/pages/lifecycle/" format="html" scope="external"><tm trademark="IBM" tmtype="reg">IBM</tm> Support Product lifecycle </xref> page, until end of support date. </p>
<p><tm trademark="IBM" tmtype="reg">IBM</tm> Support offerings can provide additional services and help to extend the life of your software investment. For more information, see <xref href="https://www.ibm.com/support/pages/node/7008589" format="html" scope="external"><tm trademark="IBM" tmtype="reg">IBM</tm> Extended Support</xref>.</p>
</body>
